What is Audiophix?

Audiophix is an interactive audio/visual experience. Mix and match your sounds and visuals with just a tap of a key. Audiophix stands for consumer advocacy and encourages community dialogue on future “soundscape” releases.

About the ceators of Audiophix

Audiophix was created by Neelam Wooley and Sam Yee. Two BCIT Digital Design and Development students from Vancouver who are passionate about the complimenting nature of art and music.

They hope you enjoy their project.
